org.apache.flink.runtime.jobgraph

Class JobOutputVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.jobgraph.AbstractJobVertex
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.jobgraph.AbstractJobOutputVertex
        • org.apache.flink.runtime.jobgraph.JobOutputVertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOReadableWritable

    public class JobOutputVertex
extends AbstractJobOutputVertex
    A JobOutputVertex is a specific sub-type of a AbstractJobOutputVertex and is designed for Nephele tasks which sink data in a not further specified way. As every job output vertex, a JobOutputVertex must not have any further output.
